#Prowling Geistcatcher (#1085, "not just dies") - PARKED, TWO REAL FINDINGS:
#  1. The @sacrificed(creature|mybattlefield) exile trigger does NOT fire when the
#     sacrifice is paid as a COST (Carrion Feeder's {S(creature)}): the sacrificed
#     bears go to the graveyard, never exiled. Suspect: cost-path sacrifices skip
#     WEventCardSacrifice (cf. the Kathari #1146 lesson - only AASacrificeCard
#     emits it). Engine item: emit the sacrifice event from the cost path too.
#  2. The return leg is scripted _DIES_ but oracle says "leaves the battlefield" -
#     the @movedto(this|nonbattlezone) from(mybattlefield) idiom is the data fix,
#     blocked on finding any way to load the exile leg first.
[INIT]
firstmain
[PLAYER1]
manapool:{R}{R}
inplay:prowling geistcatcher,carrion feeder,grizzly bears
hand:shock,shock
[PLAYER2]
[DO]
carrion feeder
grizzly bears
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
choice 0
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
shock
prowling geistcatcher
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
shock
prowling geistcatcher
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
choice 0
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
[ASSERT]
FIRSTMAIN
[PLAYER1]
inplay:carrion feeder,grizzly bears
graveyard:shock,shock,prowling geistcatcher
[PLAYER2]
[END]
